	            + "    ) AS a WHERE row_seq BETWEEN (("+page+" - 1) * "+itemCountPerPage+") +1 AND "+page+" * "+itemCountPerPage+" ";
	    return (List<User>)this.jdbcTemplate.query(query, this.userMapper2);
	}
	
	
	
